name: Verify the "Managing Provider" is able to create "Other Provider" when all the fields are populated with valid data

steps.name: When I click on the second index button Other Providers
Then It redirects on the Other Providers screen
Then Search and delete duplicate data Auto_Test_Other_Provider
When I click on the button with text New Other Provider
Then It redirects on the New Other Provider screen
When I click on the button with text Create
When User add Auto_Test_Other_Provider in name field
When I fill valid and unique data in email
When User add pediatricians in specialty field
When User add 2026839019 in mobile number field
When User add https://webdriver.io in website field
When User add 2026839019 in office number field
When User add IT Office in office information field
When User add Bridgeland in State field
When User add Silverstone in city field
When User add Westwood Park, TX 24680 in address field
When User add 10001 in zipcode field
When I click on the button with text Create
Then Success message Other Provider Added Succesfully. Credentials will be sent to an email ! appears
When I populate data Auto_Test_Other_Provider in the "Search" field
Then A "Other Provider" gets created and it displays on the "Other Providers" list with pediatricians and Auto_Test_Other_Provider and Active
